Package: hgwellsr
Type: Package
Title: Data package of selected H. G. Wells novels
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Erik", "Howard", email="erikhoward@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Maintainer: Erik Howard <erikhoward@protonmail.com>
Description: Full text data for selected H. G. Wells novels ready for data analysis.
    This includes the novels Ann Vernnica, The History of Mr Polly, The Invisible Man,
    The Island of Doctor Moreau, The Time Machine and The War of the Worlds.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/erikhoward/hgwellsr
